verbose_text: It is also worth noting that our unstimulated sera concentrations of IFN-gamma, IL-1beta, and IL-7 were significantly reduced pretreatment in the P4 group, and IFN-gamma and IL-7 were also comparatively reduced at 28 weeks, suggesting that the effects were P4 related.
